                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/2390: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-01-19T16:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 19, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>7. Department’s telegram no. 340 of December 24, 1921, 3 p.m. Confidentially
                    inform the British Minister regarding tentative plan outlined in that telegram
                    for the temporary conservation of the Chinese Eastern. Secure from him such
                    cooperation as you may think best for the purpose of winning for the plan its
                    acceptance by the leaders in the present Chinese Government. Important
                    concessions to China are embodied in the proposal outlined which under the
                    circumstances in the opinion of the Department represents an arrangement as
                    favorable as China reasonably can expect. The Department is informing the
                    British delegation here regarding the plan and it is expected that in due course
                    your British colleague will receive instructions.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
